__[Alexandra Gavillet](https://instagram.com/alexandra_gavillet/%29)__   
@alexandra_gavillet  

With photographs manipulated to appear as software glitches and an abundance of 3-D gifs, recent NYU grad Alexandra Gavillet’s images push the boundaries of image-viewing in the digital age. Having shot models (such as Cara Delevingne, to name one), this NYFW photographer will be right at home on the runway.
